+ #                              ||| /     delay
+ #           TASK-PID     CPU#  ||||   TIMESTAMP  FUNCTION
+ #              | |         |   ||||      |         |
+          <idle>-0       [015] dN...  4995.979886: amd_pstate_perf: amd_min_perf=85 amd_des_perf=85 amd_max_perf=166 cpu_id=15 changed=false fast_switch=true
